com.qtfx.lib.gui

Class FieldControl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.qtfx.lib.gui.FieldControl
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CheckBoxField, ChoiceBoxField, ComboBoxField, DatePickerField, LookupComboBoxField, NumberTextField, PasswordTextField, StringTextField

    public abstract class FieldControl
extends java.lang.Object
    Root of controls to edit fields. Extenders should define the FX control and override setValue, call the super method and set the control value.
    Author:
    Miquel Sas
